title: Never Say Die - Volume 26
description:
The Belgian wunderkind is at it again, and this time he dropped his 2nd NSD mix,the Eptic - Never Say Die volume 26. He brings it hard with a mix of new and old dubstep, drum n bass, and closes it all out with a little bit of moombahton. Full Tracklist and Free Download Below.

On top of that I added on his newly released Eptic - Stick Up VIP. I honestly didn't think this track could go any harder than it already does, but DAMN he made it happen. I just love this kids style, and everything he drops has such a sick production value to it.
